# TODO:
# j-b on #videolan:
# Ubuntu 14.04 is the oldest version supported by VLC 3
# <j-b> use extras/tools;
# <j-b> use contribs (for alsa)
# <j-b> use contribs with --disable to disable bluray
# <j-b> don't disable cddb
